{"tid":794556,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[學日文] 有無邊本日文書，係教完一個文形/章節，就有一堆練習畀你做？","createTime":"2018-08-26T10:39:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-27T09:25:10.000Z","uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ba825bd5bd17eab452e02a7264570f7dd59397ba","tid":794556,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T10:39:59.000Z","msg":"小弟學緊日文<br />\n見到市面上日文書好多   琳瑯滿目<br />\nJLPT既模擬試題都多<br />\n但係分chapters既練習就少好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">想問下，有無邊本書，係教一個文形/一個chapter，然後一堆exercises跟尾畀你做？</span><br />\n等你可以學左少少野，立即有機會practice一輪<br />\n<br />\n例如話，<br />\n學完「動詞ない形」，就立即有10題「動詞ない形」例題畀你練，有埋答案<br />\n學完「動詞た形」，就立即有10題「動詞た形」題目做<br />\n咁樣去畀你即學即練  打好根基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔知各位大佬  知唔知有咁既日文教材呢？<br />\n畀個書名等我買都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f07d5810fdfce18a0dff5f5689bade5f3148fc5","tid":794556,"uid":62628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-26T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"みんなの日本語"},{"pid":"aff905ea14f3600eb875d5cf56743cc3d4fbddee","tid":794556,"uid":133896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:11:42.000Z","msg":"Genki 1 Textbook: An Integrated Course in Elementary Japanese / 初級日本語「げんき」<br />\n有額外練習本，search reddit"},{"pid":"5c5a492203e389aabe447dc1df045297ccb688f5","tid":794556,"uid":113250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T09:25:10.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}